			You will need to install the <a target="_blank" onclick="return openAppPage('Geo+Location+Lookup+Script');" href="http://apps.splunk.com/app/291/">Geolocation Lookup</a> app in order to translate external IPs to Geo info for the flash maps and geo based reports to work.

